- [ ] Tests written or updated
- [ ] Code implemented
- [ ] API contracts updated
- [ ] Permissions tested
- [ ] Audit events tested
- [ ] Visual evidence saved
- [ ] Tests/typecheck/lint/build passed
- [ ] Risk assessment completed
- [ ] Handoff updated
- [ ] State updated
- [ ] Commit created only after passing gates

